description: The video shows a cartoon image of a fair-skinned woman with blonde, wavy hair in a vintage style. She is wearing a strapless green dress and has a green bow in her hair. She is smiling broadly with bright red lips. She is holding a multi-layered cake with pink frosting, blueberries, and green leaves on a silver platter. There is a lit candle on top of the cake. The background is a light blue circle with sparkling white stars and colorful triangular pennants hanging around the top. The candle flame flickers and dances slightly.
